[[萨尔瓦多·达利|萨尔瓦多·达利]]深深着迷于阿尔钦博托的作品并深受其画风影响。他最著名的“隐藏的面孔”是《Slave Market with the Disappearing Bust of Voltaire》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://psyc.queensu.ca/~psyc382/daliSlavemarket.html |title=Salvador Dalí: Slave Market with the Disappearing Bust of Voltaire |publisher=psyc.queensu.ca |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120524054916/http://psyc.queensu.ca/~psyc382/daliSlavemarket.html |archivedate=2012-05-24 }}</ref>，画面中隐藏了[[伏尔泰|伏尔泰]]半身像。

其他尝试过创作隐藏的面孔的超现实主义画家：
*[[马克斯·恩斯特|马克斯·恩斯特]]
*[[雷内·马格利特|雷内·马格利特]]

István Orosz尝试将扭曲立体投影图（anamorphosis）与“隐藏的面孔”结合。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gallery-diabolus.com/gallery/upload/utisz/Verne00.jpg |title=Anamorphosis with double meanings: landscape and portrait of Jules Verne in the mirror cylinder |publisher=gallery-diabolus.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927070312/http://www.gallery-diabolus.com/gallery/upload/utisz/Verne00.jpg |archivedate=2007-09-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gallery-diabolus.com/gallery/upload/utisz/shakespeareszinhaz.jpg |title=Anamorphosis with double meanings: a theatre and portrait of William Shakespeare.（View from a narrow angle!） |publisher=gallery-diabolus.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927070135/http://www.gallery-diabolus.com/gallery/upload/utisz/shakespeareszinhaz.jpg |archivedate=2007-09-27 }}</ref>

